<p>Quick Tips start this episode, including topics like macOS Sierra&#039;s picture-in-picture videos, auto-logout, Sierra upgrade hints, macerror, cleaning up your Keychain, printing to PDF on &lt;em&gt;any&lt;/em&gt; iOS 10 device, Apple Watch battery life and more. Then it&#039;s on to questions about macOS Sierra&#039;s network login changes, running a mixed macOS and OS X household and, finally, a discussion about lightning strikes and how to recover. Enjoy!Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
